{"tid":1987414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2019年4月25日　林鄭：提出修訂逃犯條例是經過審慎研究","createTime":"2020-04-24T12:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:43:20.000Z","uid":142878,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93341df303b8af78cbda2c5f287e2088b7dac0f2","tid":1987414,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:31:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2019年</span></span></strong>4月25日 <br />\n林鄭：提出修訂逃犯條例是經過審慎研究<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥回應楊岳橋提出私人條例草案，重申政府提出修訂逃犯條例是經過審慎研究，立法會應該審議政府提出的草案。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥亦回應佔中案被告的刑期說尊重法庭的判決，又指有關案件可能再進入司法程序，特區政府不宜評論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=345791&amp;past=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345791%26past%3D1&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=1973620d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345791%26past%3D1&h=55e344e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=345791&amp;past=1</a>"},{"pid":"6621ebc50c89e0b17fbc661db2720bf4e8790cc6","tid":1987414,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04836603e0f6c678e00a6fa6a260bfb2d63351c9","tid":1987414,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"記住仲有民建聯份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df1d14d4ada455181567fe0615d4e1fd613aeb0","tid":1987414,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"個研究係咪想搵方法可以激發曬香港人嘅反抗意識出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返2014年，當年根本係Bb班<br />\n今次呢啲先似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" cla